PortSystem          1.0
PortGroup           python 1.0
PortGroup           github 1.0
PortGroup           boost 1.0

github.setup        schrodinger pymol-open-source 2.5.0 v
revision            4
name                pymol
conflicts           pymol-devel

categories          science chemistry
platforms           darwin
universal_variant   no
license             PSF
